ong recorded in transmitted sources. Therefore, it is very likely that this is a unique contemporary testimony of the movement, of which our pilgrim was also part. Complementing extant historical sources, the manuscript provides evidence for the high degree of ethnic, cultural and linguistic diversity in Western China during this period.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 08. Jul 2019) 0aBuddhist pilgrims and pilgrimageszChina. 0aBuddhist pilgrims and pilgrimageszTibet Region. 4aChina. 4aHandschriften. 4aManuscripts. 4aTibet. 70(DE-601)1045228600(DE-588)4064460-1aWallfahrt2gnd 70(DE-601)1063668230(DE-588)4008690-2aBuddhismus2gnd 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh1 aGalambos, Imre, eauthor.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Philosophy English Language 2000-2014z978311023848808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2011z9783110261189oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2011z978311026123308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET PHILOSOPHIE UND GESCHICHTE 2011z9783110261257oZDB-23-DGE0 cprintz978311022564840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110225655423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110225655.jpg  a978-3-11-023848-8  DGBA Backlist Philosophy English Language 2000-2014c2000d2014  a978-3-11-026123-3  E-BOOK PACKAGE ENGLISH LANGUAGES TITLES 2011b2011  aDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKAL